OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fodd one could be heavy and thundery.
OL,7,FBest of the sunshine in the afternoon
OL,8,Facross western Argyll and the Isles.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA bright end to the day with
OL,11,Fscattered showers, these will die out
OL,12,Ffor a time. Cloud increasing overnight
OL,13,Fwith more showers arriving from the
OL,14,Fwest.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FIt will be another day of
OL,17,Fbright spells and showers, some
OL,18,Fperhaps heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
